ComicInfo.Series: Cosmic Ghost Rider Destroys Marvel History
ComicInfo.Summary: The aftermath of Frank Castle’s fateful clash with the mob! As the smoke clears, only one family is left standing…but can Frank live with the changes he’s made to his own history? And more importantly, can the timestream? Find out in this epic conclusion!
